{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"double","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:d"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"zoomLevel","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In addition to affecting the visual size and detail of features on the map,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the zoom level affects the size of the vector tiles that are loaded. At zoom","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"level 0, each tile covers the entire world map; at zoom level 1, it covers ¼","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the world; at zoom level 2, ","type":"text"},{"text":"1","type":"text"},{"text":"⁄","type":"text"},{"text":"16","type":"text"},{"text":" of the world, and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"so on.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view immediately. If you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"want to animate the change, use the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setZoomLevel:animated:"},{"text":" method instead.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/zoomLevel","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/zoomlevel"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"text":"The zoom level of the receiver.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)zoomLevel","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"zoomLevel","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"zoomLevel","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1026","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"zoomLevel"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","title":"MLNMapView","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/zoomLevel":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The zoom level of the receiver.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/zoomLevel","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/zoomlevel","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"zoomLevel","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"zoomLevel"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","type":"topic","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol"}}}